     fhir:div [ fhir:v "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: CodeSystem claim-decision</b></p><a name=\"claim-decision\"> </a><a name=\"hcclaim-decision\"> </a><p>This case-sensitive code system <code>http://hl7.org/fhir/claim-decision</code> defines the following codes:</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">denied<a name=\"claim-decision-denied\"> </a></td><td>Denied</td><td>The claim, or individual services, are not approved for any payment. This may also be known as 'rejected'.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">approved<a name=\"claim-decision-approved\"> </a></td><td>Approved</td><td>The claim, or individual services, are approved as submitted.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">partial<a name=\"claim-decision-partial\"> </a></td><td>Partial</td><td>The claim, or individual services, are approved at an amount less than as submitted.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">pending<a name=\"claim-decision-pending\"> </a></td><td>Pending</td><td>The adjudication processing is not complete. This may be due to requiring manual review or receipt of additional information.</td></tr></table></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
